divs: Sighting Detailsi was outside and looked up and saw a star like object which was high it was traveling too fast to be a plane and had no flashing lights on it , it was a perfect clear night and i could see orion stars and the plough this object traveled between thease two in around 4 seconds , it also looked like it was seriously high , im not sure if it could have been a satalite maybe ? from where i was looking it moved left through the sky i couldnt sleep so i did some laundry and went out to hang it on the line a star but then saw it was moving , then thought it could be a satalite or space station passing over , but this thing was moving fast !! moved across the sky from left to right at a realy high speed it took only a few seconds to cover the distance a jumbo jet covers in minutes ! this is not the first sighting i have had i had a very close sighting about 10 years ago while with a friend who is a fire fighter so not shocked but i am always critical of what i see as i no there are many things like chinese lanterns , aircraft , satalites , etc in the skys if it had been moving slower id have passed it as maybe a plane or satalight , but this moved so fast and smooth in a perfect line it had no trails coming from it either
Summary: star like object traveling at high speed
